content_html: Kathmandu, Sept 16: The low-pressure monsoon trough is in its average position at present and there is also an impact of water vapor from the Arab Sea and the Bay of Bengal, according to the Weather Forecasting Division. The Division stated that the weather shall remain generally cloudy nationwide today and some area
